        <description>
            <geninfo>
                <para>The Models listed above that are equipped with the optional snow valve air cleaner, Codes 12VAG or
                    12VAL, can be retrofitted with a new design, higher torque, snow door motor.
                </para>
                <specpara>
                    <note>
                        <para>Do not replace the air cleaner housing unless you experience snow valve binding after
                            replacing with the improved torque snow valve motor assembly.
                        </para>
                    </note>
                </specpara>
            </geninfo>
        </description>
